{"tid":1063560,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"被愛既人真係好幸福","createTime":"2019-03-16T00:37:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-16T04:16:45.000Z","uid":193275,"like":36,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4debbed72807abf2b57a1216cf87cfaac7a1310c","tid":1063560,"uid":193275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T00:37:01.000Z","msg":"一直都好羨慕其他人會有人無條件地愛自己<br />\n會有人願意為自己去付出 所有野以你為先 <br />\n想盡辦法去氹自己開心 盡量去滿足自己<br />\n我真係覺得有人愛自己真係一件好幸福既事<br />\n我都好想感受一下被愛既感覺<br />\n我都好想拍一段轟轟烈烈既拖<br />\n但偏偏自己犯賤 被虐<br />\n選擇做一個卑微既人 明明缺愛 仲要為一個唔值得既人去無條件地付出 比愛對方 令對方開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以被愛既你地 真係要好好珍惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9747ef675e2a312103d4d2c514ab25a295d7ccb5","tid":1063560,"uid":70292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T00:44:19.000Z","msg":"珍惜ing<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d63b6b7eca3942d3b5bf0e5110cca9f9cc49e56","tid":1063560,"uid":229024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T00:50:28.000Z","msg":"珍惜緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8babf32e55e5946010fd9e51858975786bd94837","tid":1063560,"uid":71496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T01:22:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bd105081f5ba129e8a3b1f5a0804af2356153ac","tid":1063560,"uid":156587,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T01:32:58.000Z","msg":"付佢老豆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />學識愛自己仲好 自己一個更開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6573e7dc1c99ff8411d2dead44165c240500d26","tid":1063560,"uid":69567,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T01:52:29.000Z","msg":"無用㗎<br />\n你幾愛佢都好，都係話變就變<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed6244ae3bd478bb98ff2cebd151fc846364dbd8","tid":1063560,"uid":43936,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T02:58:30.000Z","msg":"無條件付出又點<br />\n當我想佢付出，佢竟然話我市儈<br />\n話真係愛就唔好期求回報<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd0c9826a2b083d4ba8f38278b19c9cdbd646f98","tid":1063560,"uid":59159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T03:10:59.000Z","msg":"一個犯殘嘅人叫人珍惜愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"456e51ca1cae0c677824a0e23493e556d8356bba","tid":1063560,"uid":1834,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T04:16:45.000Z","msg":"樓主是咪寧願做人第三者都唔做人女朋友"}]}